Class Summary
DefaultNail The default nail class used by the server when an invalid command (nonexisting classname or alias) is issued.
NGAlias Provides a means to view and add aliases.
NGClasspath Provides a means to display and add to the system classpath at runtime.
NGServerStats Displays all NailStats tracked by the server.
NGStop Shuts down the currently running server.
NGVersion Displays the version of the NailGun server and exits.
